---
---

<section class="relative h-screen min-h-[700px] flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden bg-brand-black">
  <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img 
      src="/images/foto_1.jpeg" 
      alt="Jardines de Finca Los Pinos" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center opacity-85"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-black via-brand-black/30 to-brand-black/50"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Vertical Grid Overlay (Reference to architectural layout) -->
  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 right-0 z-10 pointer-events-none hidden md:grid grid-cols-4 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="border-l border-brand-white/5 h-full"></div>
    <div class="border-l border-brand-white/5 h-full"></div>
    <div class="border-l border-brand-white/5 h-full"></div>
    <div class="border-l border-brand-white/5 border-r h-full"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Header Bar -->
  <header class="relative z-30 w-full px-6 py-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between">
    <a href="#" class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-brand-white tracking-wide">Finca Los Pinos</a>
    <nav class="hidden lg:flex gap-8 text-brand-white/80 font-medium text-sm tracking-wide">
      <a href="#galeria" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Galería</a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Qué Incluye</a>
      <a href="#tarifas" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Tarifas</a>
      <a href="#proveedores" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Proveedores</a>
      <a href="#faq" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Preguntas</a>
      <a href="#contacto" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Contacto</a>
    </nav>
    <button 
      onclick="window.openChatbot && window.openChatbot()"
      class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-brand-white hover:bg-brand-crema text-brand-black font-semibold rounded text-sm transition-all duration-300 shadow-md flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"
    >
      <span>Reservar Visita</span>
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 00-2 2z"/></svg>
    </button>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Headline & Features Content -->
  <div class="relative z-20 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between pb-12 pt-8">
    <!-- Spacer -->
    <div></div>

    <!-- Main Headline Area -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl text-left mt-auto">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-gold/20 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-gold/30 text-brand-gold text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
        <span>★ 7 Años Consecutivos Wedding Awards (2020-2026) ★</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-brand-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-md">
        EL ESCENARIO DE <span class="text-brand-gold italic font-accent lowercase text-6xl md:text-8xl block md:inline font-normal leading-none">vuestros</span> SUEÑOS
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-brand-white/80 font-light mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow">
        Un enclave natural exclusivo en Firgas con capacidad para 300 invitados. Vuestra celebración rodeada de frondosas arboledas, jardines y rincones con encanto.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center w-full sm:w-auto">
        <button 
          onclick="window.openChatbot && window.openChatbot()"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary/90 text-brand-white font-medium rounded transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl text-md flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
        >
          Consultar Disponibilidad
        </button>
        <a 
          href="#tarifas" 
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-brand-white font-medium rounded border border-brand-white/20 hover:border-brand-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 text-md text-center"
        >
          Ver Tarifas 2027
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Features Panel (Asymmetric & Structured like reference image) -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-end mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-brand-white/10">
      <!-- Gold Highlight Box (Left) -->
      <div class="bg-brand-gold p-6 rounded-lg text-brand-black shadow-2xl flex flex-col gap-3 border border-brand-gold/30">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-black/60">Características clave:</span>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-brand-black/10 pb-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold">Capacidad Máx.</span>
          <span class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold leading-none">300 pax</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold">Ubicación</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-right">Firgas, Gran Canaria</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Description Block (Center) -->
      <div class="text-brand-white/60 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed pb-1">
        <p>A tan solo 20 minutos de Las Palmas de Gran Canaria, Finca Los Pinos combina la exclusividad de una casa rural de ensueño con espectaculares jardines diseñados para bodas memorables.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Ratings (Right) -->
      <div class="flex justify-start md:justify-end items-center gap-4 text-brand-white pb-1">
        <div class="text-left md:text-right">
          <span class="block text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-brand-gold">4.9 / 5</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-white/60">181 opiniones en Bodas.net</span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-brand-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-gold bg-brand-white/5 backdrop-blur">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

